{"tid":1798824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有普選，唯有獨立","createTime":"2019-12-26T13:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T17:08:36.000Z","uid":212731,"like":167,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"c130c5f877b0ef84140cb273a55e232d48072a03","tid":1798824,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:34:47.000Z","msg":"驚五大訴求同香港獨立有衝突？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚會分散焦點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，點解唔試下將兩個方向拉埋一齊講？<br />\n普選同獨立，一個口號講晒兩個香港關鍵最需要既野<br />\n咁咪唔使驚有衝突，唔使驚分散焦點，講清楚晒香港人需要Ｄ乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有普選，唯有獨立</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7f2f9b600bd89f8e1f06ef62d359bf4697afcb33","tid":1798824,"uid":139700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"楊逸朗：「無論有幾多阻礙都好，我哋香港獨派都唔會放棄，一路堅持到底」<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eGGrdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eGGrdS</a>"},{"pid":"d7c025b4f821ad3f8203d67545025db72c9b2d49","tid":1798824,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:35:45.000Z","msg":"g持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26fc550f7f39cdc07772056e94fbbc872255e7f","tid":1798824,"uid":212731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:35:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有普選，唯有獨立</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cc6532b76f970a27e3d3701ee5b3d213cb64af5d","tid":1798824,"uid":295452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:36:38.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"b460dd6eb79cf1db8896e41a3cb7fd1aa032088c","tid":1798824,"uid":73143,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T13:37:04.000Z","msg":"